ier published two controversial research studies<sup id=\"cite_ref-Coghlan_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"http:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Luc_Montagnier#cite_note-Coghlan-3\"><span>[<\/span>3<span>]<\/span><\/a><\/sup> that some homeopaths claimed as support for <a href=\"http:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Homeopathy\" title=\"Homeopathy\">homeopathy<\/a>. Although Montagnier disputed any such support,<sup id=\"cite_ref-cbc_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"http:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Luc_Montagnier#cite_note-cbc-4\"><span>[<\/span>4<span>]<\/span><\/a><\/sup> many scientists greeted his claims with scorn and harsh criticism.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Coghlan_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"http:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Luc_Montagnier#cite_note-Coghlan-3\"><span>[<\/span>3<span>]<\/span><\/a><\/sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-PZ_Myers_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"http:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Luc_Montagnier#cite_note-PZ_Myers-5\"><span>[<\/span>5<span>]<\/span><\/a><\/sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-NS_editorial_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"http:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Luc_Montagnier#cite_note-NS_editorial-6\"><span>[<\/span>6<span>]<\/span><\/a><\/sup><\/p>","name":"Luc Montagnier","place_of_birth":"Chabris , France","place_of_death":null,"text":"Luc Montagnier , Physiology or Medicine, 2008","year":2008.0}